<html>
<head>
	<title></title>
</head>
<body style="height: auto; min-height: auto;">
<style type="text/css">.table_header{
            font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;
            font-size:11pt;
			background-color: #F2F2F2;
            font-weight:bold;
		}
        #bodyStyle{
			font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;
            font-size:11pt;
			height: auto; 
			min-height: auto;
		}
		#interestTable{
            font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;
            font-size:11pt;
			width:90%;
			margin-left: auto;
			margin-right: auto;
		}
		#interestTable td{
			border: 1px solid black ;
			text-align:center; 
			vertical-align:top; 
			background-color:#e2f0d9; 
			
		}
		#taskTable{
            font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;
            font-size:11pt;
			width:90%;
			margin-left: auto;
			margin-right: auto;
		}
		#taskTable td{
			border: 1px solid black ;
			text-align:center; 
			vertical-align:top; 			
		}
</style>
<div id="bodyStyle"><span>Dear <strong>{{{Recipient.FirstName}}},</strong><br />
<br />
I had a&nbsp;<strong>{{{Meeting_Note__c.Meeting_Type__c}}}</strong> with&nbsp;{{{Meeting_Note__c.CompanyName__c}}} on&nbsp;<strong>{{{Meeting_Note__c.Date__c}}}.</strong></span><br />
<br />
<span>Please find below the minutes of&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>{{{Meeting_Note__c.Name}}} :&nbsp;</strong></span><br />
&nbsp;
<table style="width:100%">
	
		<tr class="table_header">
			<th colspan="3" id="companyAttTitle" style="text-align: left;"><b>Attendees from Client</b></th>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="3">
			<ul id="companyAttList">
				<li>Client 1</li>
				<li>Client 2</li>
			</ul>
			</td>
		</tr>
	
</table>

<table style="width:100%">
	
		<tr class="table_header">
			<th colspan="3" style="text-align: left;"><b>Attendees from Carmignac</b></th>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="3">
			<ul id="carmiAttList">
				<li>Carmi 1</li>
				<li>Carmi 2</li>
			</ul>
			</td>
		</tr>
	
</table>

<table id="interestTableHeader" style="width:100%">
	
		<tr class="table_header">
			<th colspan="3" style="text-align: left;"><b>Products discussed</b></th>
		</tr>
	
</table>
&nbsp;

<table id="interestTable">
	<colgroup>
		<col span="2" />
	</colgroup>
	<tbody id="interestLines">
		<tr>
			<td><span>Name</span></td>
			<td><span>Interest</span></td>
		</tr>
	
</table>
&nbsp;

<table id="taskTableHeader" style="width:100%">
	
		<tr class="table_header">
			<th colspan="3" style="text-align: left;"><b>Action Plan</b></th>
		</tr>
	
</table>
&nbsp;

<table id="taskTable">
	<colgroup>
		<col span="1" />
	</colgroup>
	<tbody id="interestLines">
		<tr>
			<td><span>Subject</span></td>
			<td><span>Description</span></td>
			<td><span>Due Date</span></td>
			<td><span>Owner</span></td>
		</tr>
	
</table>
&nbsp;

<table style="width:100%">
	
		<tr class="table_header">
			<th colspan="3" style="text-align: left;"><b>Notes</b></th>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="3">{{{Meeting_Note__c.Note__c}}}</td>
		</tr>
	
</table>
<br />
<br />
Thank you,<br />
{{{Sender.Name}}}</div>
</body>
</html>